query:
SELECT id, email, firstName, enneagramType, 
LENGTH(enneagram_analysis) as analysis_length,
createdAt 
FROM conversations 
WHERE enneagram_analysis IS NOT NULL 
ORDER BY createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 3;
